{
  "page": "Lord Seneschal of Highgarden",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Lord Seneschal of Highgarden</b> is a title held by <a href=\"/index.php/Garth_Tyrell\" title=\"Garth Tyrell\">Garth Tyrell</a> since the rule of <a href=\"/index.php/Luthor_Tyrell\" title=\"Luthor Tyrell\">Luthor Tyrell</a>, the late <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Paramount_of_the_Mander\" title=\"Lord Paramount of the Mander\">Lord Paramount of the Mander</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Highgarden\" title=\"Lord of Highgarden\">Lord of Highgarden</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Warden_of_the_South\" title=\"Warden of the South\">Warden of the South</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc7.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc7.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_Seneschal_of_Highgarden&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: See also\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/High_Steward\" title=\"High Steward\">High Steward</a>, a similar title once held by <a href=\"/index.php/House_Tyrell\" title=\"House Tyrell\">House Tyrell</a> during the reign of the <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Reach\" title=\"King of the Reach\">Kings of the Reach</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Gardener\" title=\"House Gardener\">House Gardener</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_Seneschal_of_Highgarden&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\"